Hi <%= @booking.user.name %>,

Your tickets for <%= @booking.show.movie.title %> are confirmed.

Reference: <%= @booking.reference %>
Theater:   <%= @booking.show.screen.theater.name %>
Screen:    <%= @booking.show.screen.name %>
Showtime:  <%= @booking.show.starts_at.in_time_zone('UTC').strftime('%d %b %Y, %H:%M UTC') %>
Seats:     <%= @booking.booking_seats.includes(:seat).map { |bs| "#{bs.seat.row_label}#{bs.seat.column_index}" }.join(', ') %>
Total:     $<%= format('%.2f', @booking.total_amount) %>

Enjoy the show!
— CineBook
